SCRIBE

   Scribe is very similar to brew. Mages and clerics can write their own 
scrolls. With a quill, parchment, and a gem to sacrifice, you can make the 
scrolls.

"Fly":		a small emerald
"Heal":		a small diamond
"Sanc"tuary:	a small ruby
Second "Wind":	a small topaz
"True Sight": 	a small sapphire

ex. scribe sanc (Makes a sanctuary scroll!)

Related Topics: SPELL INFO, OBJECT MANIPULATION
